@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.exp(v2 + 0.31) * 0.39))
    v0 = (v2 - v0)
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.03) * (v1 + 0.56 - tmp + 0.09)) * v2)
    v2 = (0.58 + (v1 + 0.89))
    tmp = v0
    tmp = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.15 / v2 + 0.50) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.73)))
    data[tid] = v0
